      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 140: Edited message history now stores bodyOverwrite instead of the original edited body, so previousBodies loses the canonical content for each edition. This makes it impossible for UI/actions that need the original text, audit/history display, or future edit operations to distinguish plugin-rendered text from the actual message content. Preserve the original body separately and only apply the overwrite at the presentation layer, matching the new OriginalBody role pattern.\n```suggestion\npreviousBodies.append(Body {edition.value(\"id\"), edition.value(\"body\"), QString(edition.value(\"timestamp\")).toInt()});\n```",
      "revId": "dd0e0ba2baab830ec4401a08c12c78b26ddc4882",
